kapan kami bisa menerbitkan bukunya?

735
00:48:36,017 --> 00:48:37,310
Masih kupikirkan.

736
00:48:37,560 --> 00:48:38,895
Sampai kapan...

737
00:48:42,273 --> 00:48:44,442
Ini Tim Editor Penerbit Gyeoroo.

738
00:48:46,111 --> 00:48:47,028
Begitu?

739
00:48:47,612 --> 00:48:48,571
Ya.

740
00:48:49,155 --> 00:48:50,240
Baik. Terima kasih.

741
00:48:50,657 --> 00:48:51,783
Pak Cha,

742
00:48:51,866 --> 00:48:54,327
buku pertama kami <i>Pikiran Tanaman</i>...

