00:54:08,641 --> 00:54:10,351
- Mereka berkencan!
- Ada apa?

868
00:54:10,476 --> 00:54:12,270
- Lihat!
- Pak Kim!

869
00:54:12,520 --> 00:54:13,896
- Mereka berkencan!
- Astaga.

