883
00:55:51,285 --> 00:55:53,704
<i>Ini buku yang aku baca paling lama.</i>

884
00:56:01,420 --> 00:56:02,505
Apa hobimu?

885
00:56:02,672 --> 00:56:04,257
Hobiku membaca buku.

886
00:56:04,340 --> 00:56:05,258
Membaca.

887
00:56:06,134 --> 00:56:08,177
Itu sebabnya kau bekerja di penerbitan.

888
00:56:08,261 --> 00:56:10,972
Ya, aku selalu ingin berada di dekat buku.

889
00:56:11,055 --> 00:56:12,974
Itulah alasanku bekerja di sini.

890
00:56:13,057 --> 00:56:14,600
Kau... Astaga, dia mengejutkanku.

891
00:56:14,684 --> 00:56:16,686
EPILOG

