00:56:21,607 --> 00:56:22,859
Kenapa pamanmu kemari?

896
00:56:24,152 --> 00:56:25,736
Sedang apa kau di sini, Ji-yul?

897
00:56:26,821 --> 00:56:28,030
Halo.

