00:56:28,114 --> 00:56:29,115
Maaf.

899
00:56:29,657 --> 00:56:30,700
Dia milikku.

900
00:56:30,783 --> 00:56:32,410
Apa? Ji-yul.

901
00:56:32,869 --> 00:56:34,912
Hei, aku sedang kencan buta!

