00:57:18,289 --> 00:57:20,124
- Terlalu asin?
- Enak.

910
00:57:22,627 --> 00:57:24,337
Astaga, kau kecil sekali.

911
00:57:24,545 --> 00:57:26,005
- Astaga.
- Jangan sentuh dia.

912
00:57:26,422 --> 00:57:28,216
